&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/LmxLORiBGlwi2S8g6PGwiCowrF5URndyOBmRSfdrp01Z-VF1SD9DPMl1an6mfI_iuHsRAaDAiLIRk3twNxdZgWberyRCJUXMYJwjE2Ut6F2tBZHJxF0Y1hqNwcfKMKaeGeM7mawndx2bF_Kv6o9AuKYTDsllU0TjA6rzbZUu9AqdXvxLZoago1dMtSf9hKnTEOldhRRuf582lKwPbN5xIdU_hXNonuMFJ-EN2ZM-dHlI_plUNxkLxIXB9HeLshwucumh5EKfzJxk_fVACYOarSw74Q/VIH1PXIdhiYZGfWDzqLu5Y3j5jcB9Vjk/9" target="_blank"&gt;以提供数十亿美元&lt;/a&gt;，以帮助支付特朗普昨晚发布&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/H9pB_u_uj9j18Y3OcckUQ5rt2Lv5W1B_piBDviwZqPnvI33QmAOjAuDN6gx1-6yLXmJjG9TxdmojpEa7QndUJy3IpWGqBx4K6BLGf2V1GZlDqNvPHai9JQguh6Q9l-XQCKXSH74qrHHBeGrsuvCcMt9HYQsyzddYC-FjGIwhsoeD0nWAupMjgPkOcYnSIhU_Hbzjy2ukR7myPPPADet_N5QH3wEnArsZhcbDFjHlBgIc-__BeDaAJ9XC9j46Xob8v4UAqZz9bXuuRPHquJcoHqCcyQ/-XKfCChJlk-oOWMN7xtj1HTpAhfbd8Fj/9" target="_blank"&gt;的参议院版本&lt;/a&gt;的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/8HmNVwDfEl5I9NM8D3uOyv50h9J0t5wR1Aup_Ivv6FK35VHljP40V7Fl8SZHVRyxiewQ4XIiXu0U583jG3rIf0ro2oIchQ3bvKnwGZxFnQHg6-P0yDoEoarnJhsvr_SCQhdjxuk9LlfCTLNqiQZDJ5VvXWEigAQySmO2YlCwAizjbjt--YldNqKqn2kr_ZuAoYvDmp1ATh9aeoApzQNeAbgOwebH03smBBfGOiow9EVAp1OHd-ftXs_VP4vH__ck30_r8w4tSEHe0BM7W-vCZs53Mg/wWBQz-umHNY9z-U_1LWy9UuPxQkKBkpo/9" target="_blank"&gt;大量减税&lt;/a&gt;和支出。德克萨斯州参议员特德·克鲁兹（Ted Cruz）提出了结束美联储向银行支付利息的权力的想法， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/OkSbOkaVsqioj4gBOsX4jv_XljmGlS8E6SY1VOLUc4snhRE1e6MJxQKi8uF01XNABrcg_6bExEK-rspDT8R6EnpKeVOe_t_gRqZ-s-1bHJZGInqzFt5jNj47F1WkcyAGjyjlTTX0gABuRkWf__b4jX_vcBqFTbjQEFFo7EPY920sanKdsS8ZgClV9Xqskkv0oo9ilfE8lb23Dp2sQAvPEDQkytRYpCFiApnrSy7ADQh489JLql1EmC5j64Ylz976Nvy5kgUBqIt5yH1-iTuQiudIoQ/1UhqSsqY7KYnck3jOM3L0VHRvdanb5Rh/9" target="_blank"&gt;认为这将在十年内节省1.1万亿美元&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;以色列的政府幸存下来，&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/goQahfgkkIKLYSxv-c2Pof_PAu-f9bV3ZuqezYPNhHv0lAbesiTyzr8nrvsk6d2N4VIc2-sVpI16fLw45Wd