; margin: auto;" width="530" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 130%; margin-top: 8px;"&gt; SpaceX Falcon 9火箭和龙航天器从NASA的肯尼迪航天中心发射。&lt;i&gt;摄影师：Eva Marie Uzcategui/彭博社&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;特朗普计划杀死&lt;/strong&gt;​​数十名NASA任务的计划威胁到&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/PZy4K65iexzICJ-e6NZYpiuaGSkDAy4CNX8iyBDDBWivYbiTA8ctVGatA5AqAZJiziIfJpq3WwIxO53giCW98ErNrcQlAOKW-Vro490yYFAvkhTNf_rb3xHZsBHzRI647EitIeOAAO_S9oZcUNebxVPFwiu8KcUrhUQMIk_URvm6NyzvyqavXB9Sv2_KnMB4vIiE1PNkGtkkq50mYmy9I8DYOzq1by80DfuKDz_nzA1SaWBxLis-qH7t1bdHug-vJp1fHTcxkYizFl3ZhsERp4a0Zw/bKu2AL9LC-d6GuxvtpHATRIWbli7RLYW/9" target="_blank"&gt;美国太空至上&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style="padding-left: 10px; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;白宫&lt;/strong&gt;呼吁将NASA的科学支出削减约50％，至39亿美元，这是一个回调的一部分，其历史上最低的资金水平，并&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/C3Qc-urqDJEY8IR8Jw9ud2gq626ktkpnm3EdDV9Y_83py8FcoNn_a2Zyw_6XWoZZEAfv7pnKeGxUob1OKx4czV6oWYX7wnXLeq_egkbl91W_6bkpBjNPlAow2p4aXUVVYcZYHcZVdF8TifGyWBbqf661Q763wU21az0_HUnG0scWvb-AProrDW1P_9DxqwyFX3vec857p89RYANtifthvYT6gzDdg9MCaqqtzAqPFgLu1Mnx50R6Jk32rNGeBmeBIWV9Sym3ujJdFCgN8c1ROqHciw/YE50SUVg3kgvDsCr9YI4Bgu1-fd9GrMg/9" target="_blank"&gt;停止了超过40多个NASA科学任务&lt;/a&gt;和项目。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;这种降低的风险加速了&lt;/strong&gt;航天局的发展，成为成为私营企业的孵化器。它已经&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/HFbwG6EZynK0Zly_jRA4MUCAM6BqpZUbnLwWz_QYuvnL4fvIPVIH5AhL0Thk9n73We5o4xGYH9T4ZjYVsmDJAcRrj5sYXzLDuPZ8FVUJgJTP43r7GlPcGq1JEXUk-O2ycg_ph9gZZOAf0pOunhnR3JClw3Z21tMiC6_oNYOSK6vrp85b2HQai0mL5fD3pNXUlDIfQ5WAFAwRUiKe1ChrDXyojzn-K5wFm0CJzCZw1uGl2n9wSYdQUP1-rWjTyaenKwUY7kqczM